        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>🎉 Features</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Search Functionality</strong> 🔍: Quickly find emojis by typing in the search bar.</li>
                <li><strong>Categorized Buttons</strong> 📂: Access emojis based on categories like Smileys, Animals, Food, and more.</li>
                <li><strong>Clipboard Copy</strong> 📋: Click on any displayed emoji to copy it to your clipboard for easy pasting.</li>
            </ul>
